replies.body:
that would be impossible to add into the game. Knockback/Knockup duration increases with animation speed. Knockbacks that last longer are animated slower, but that's it. height always stays the same, therefore it would not really make a difference.

Besides, adding more damage to CC that already has damage doesn't Sound like much of a good idea.

while i like the concept, it is not possible in a game where everything that isn't a dash is already a set distance. (except for trist r knockback that increases with r lvl)
